title: [Catacombs, Sewers]
description: The low uneven ceiling with jagged protrusions makes walking upright burdensome.

The low uneven ceiling with jagged protrusions makes walking upright burdensome.  An almost new helmet sits on its base in the corner of the room.  Closer inspection shows a decapitated head with glossed over eyes raised to the ceiling seeing nothing.  In a small nook of the chamber the remaining dismembered body parts of the corpse rest silently.  Small armies of rodents scamper, with high-pitched squeals, back into a hole in the ground.
